PN,38601
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1772118239
OL,3,CWorker in fatal fire lived in
OL,4,C'property unfit for human habitation'
OL,6,FA Filipino migrant worker who died
OL,7,Fafter lighting a fire to keep warm was
OL,8,Fliving in a "property unfit for human
OL,9,Fhabitation", an inquest has heard.
OL,11,FGeorge Michael Monte De Ramos
OL,12,FCastrudes, 37, was killed by the blaze
OL,13,Fat his accommodation on Jersey's La
OL,14,FValette Nurseries farm in January 2025
OL,15,F- he suffered a hypoxic brain injury
OL,16,Fcaused by carbon monoxide poisoning.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1772118239
OL,3,CWorker in fatal fire lived in
OL,4,C'property unfit for human habitation'
OL,6,FRobert Cragg, an Environmental Health
OL,7,FOfficer for the Government of Jersey,
OL,8,Ftold the court there was "insufficient
OL,9,Fheating to keep the unit warm" and it
OL,10,Fwas "impossible to heat in a cost-
OL,11,Feffective manner".
OL,13,FHe explained that without heating, the
OL,14,Fcabin's base temperature was just 0.3
OL,15,Fdegrees Celsius - which is not a
OL,16,Fhabitable level.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1772118239
OL,3,CWorker in fatal fire lived in
OL,4,C'property unfit for human habitation'
OL,6,FMr Cragg said the smoke detector was
OL,7,Falso not working at the time of the
OL,8,Ffire, and it is the landlord's
OL,9,Fresponsibility to ensure minimum
OL,10,Fstandards are met.
OL,12,FHowever, due to a loophole in Jersey
OL,13,Flaw, most properties which are
OL,14,Fcurrently licensed for rent do not
OL,15,Flegally have to meet these
OL,16,Frequirements until permits are renewed
OL,17,Funder the tougher regulations.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1772118239
OL,3,CWorker in fatal fire lived in
OL,4,C'property unfit for human habitation'
OL,6,FHe admitted there have been no
OL,7,Ftargeted inspections of farm worker
OL,8,Faccommodation in Jersey since Mr
OL,9,FCastrudes' death over a year ago.
OL,11,FMr Cragg stated they would like to
OL,12,Finspect every property "over a period
OL,13,Fof years" but with a team of eight
OL,14,Fofficers, "Rome wasn't built in a day".
OL,16,FAdrian Aquino, who had previously
OL,17,Fworked and lived with Mr Castrudes on
OL,18,Fthe farm, told the inquest in St
OL,19,FHelier that their "one small heater
OL,20,Fwas not enough".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1772118239
OL,3,CWorker in fatal fire lived in
OL,4,C'property unfit for human habitation'
OL,6,FHe said the farmer, Nigel John Blake,
OL,7,Fknew the accommodation was cold and
OL,8,Fthat they asked him for thicker
OL,9,Fbedding but were told they needed to
OL,10,Fbuy it for themselves.
OL,12,FHe added that the farmer had offered
OL,13,Fthem a larger heater but Mr Castrudes
OL,14,Frefused as he was worried about the
OL,15,Felectric bill and would unplug their
OL,16,Fsmall unit at 3am to save money.
OL,18,FNigel Blake told the inquest that he
OL,19,Fhad given them a blanket and jumpers
OL,20,Fto keep them warm.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1772118239
OL,3,CWorker in fatal fire lived in
OL,4,C'property unfit for human habitation'
OL,6,FMr Aquino explained that Mr Castrudes
OL,7,Fhad resorted to sleeping in the farm's
OL,8,Fgreenhouse because it was warmer than
OL,9,Ftheir cabin.
OL,11,FHe stated that the washing machine
OL,12,Fdrum where Mr Castrudes started the
OL,13,Ffatal blaze had been given to them by
OL,14,Fthe farmer to use as a fire pit, but
OL,15,Fhe had told them "strictly to use it
OL,16,Foutside on the grass ... don't use it
OL,17,Fnear accommodation".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1772118239
OL,3,CWorker in fatal fire lived in
OL,4,C'property unfit for human habitation'
OL,6,FMr Aquino said the pair had been
OL,7,Fwarned about removing the battery from
OL,8,Fthe cabin's smoke alarm by the farmer,
OL,9,Fwho told them it was illegal.
OL,11,FMr Aquino admitted they had taken the
OL,12,Fbattery out previously as the fire
OL,13,Falarm sound was too loud when they
OL,14,Fwere cooking.
OL,16,FMr Aquino moved out six days before
OL,17,Fthe fire.
OL,19,FAt the time of the fire, Mr Castrudes
OL,20,Fis believed to have been alone in the
OL,21,Fcabin.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1772118239
OL,3,CWorker in fatal fire lived in
OL,4,C'property unfit for human habitation'
OL,6,FThe inquest heard that Jersey's Fire
OL,7,FService determined there was a battery
OL,8,Fin the cabin's fire alarm, but its
OL,9,Fpower was too low to work effectively,
OL,10,Fand it is the landlord's
OL,11,Fresponsibility to ensure it is working.
OL,13,FNigel Blake said he only checked the
OL,14,Ffire alarm once, in May 2021, and that
OL,15,Fthe tenants "never raised concerns
OL,16,Fabout the quality of accommodation or
OL,17,Fany issues with smoke detectors".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1772118239
OL,3,CWorker in fatal fire lived in
OL,4,C'property unfit for human habitation'
OL,6,FNigel Blake said Mr Castrudes was
OL,7,Femployed as an agricultural worker on
OL,8,Fa nine-month fixed contract when he
OL,9,Fdied.
OL,11,FHe described him as an "excellent
OL,12,Femployee" who "never gave me cause for
OL,13,Fconcern" and added that the Blake
OL,14,Ffamily are closing the farm
OL,15,Fpermanently this week.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1772118239
OL,3,CWorker in fatal fire lived in
OL,4,C'property unfit for human habitation'
OL,6,FDetective Constable Paul Lovesey from
OL,7,Fthe States of Jersey Police Financial
OL,8,FCrimes Unit told the inquiry that Mr
OL,9,FCastrudes was paid at least four times
OL,10,Fa month by the Blakes and received
OL,11,Fjust under #16,000 before deductions
OL,12,Fbetween January 2024 and January 2025
OL,13,F- which complies with the island's
OL,14,Fminimum wage.
OL,16,FHowever, Mr Castrudes was only paid on
OL,17,Ftime once during this period, usually
OL,18,Freceiving his salary a couple of days
OL,19,Flate.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G10/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1772118239
OL,3,CWorker in fatal fire lived in
OL,4,C'property unfit for human habitation'
OL,6,FMr Lovesey revealed that Mr Castrudes
OL,7,Falso sent three-quarters of his 2024
OL,8,Fsalary to his family back home in the
OL,9,FPhilippines.
OL,11,FMr Lovesey concluded that it was Mr
OL,12,FCastrudes's choice to do this and "had
OL,13,Fhe not been sending a big proportion
OL,14,Fof his income home, he would have been
OL,15,Fable to afford electricity".
OL,17,FPaul Blake, who owns La Valette
OL,18,FNurseries in Grouville with Nigel and
OL,19,FDavid Blake, also provided a statement
OL,20,Fto the inquiry.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G11/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1772118239
OL,3,CWorker in fatal fire lived in
OL,4,C'property unfit for human habitation'
OL,6,FHe said that Mr Castrudes worked a
OL,7,Fminimum of 40 hours a week and longer
OL,8,Fin the summer.
OL,10,FPaul Blake added that no issues were
OL,11,Freported with the accommodation and
OL,12,Fthey charged Mr Castrudes and Mr
OL,13,FAquino a total of around #1,000 per
OL,14,Fmonth for the cabin, plus electricity
OL,15,Fbills.
OL,17,FThe inquest continues, with a verdict
OL,18,Fexpected on Friday (27 February).
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G12/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
